[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[ \left( \frac{s}{C} + \frac{D - s}{W} \right) + \left( \frac{D - s}{W} + \frac{s}{C} \right) = 52 \text{ minutes} \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Simplifying, we get:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[ 2 \left( \frac{s}{C} + \frac{D - s}{W} \right) = 52 \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m We know:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[ \frac{D}{C} = 10 \text{ minutes} \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[ \frac{D}{W} = 30 \text{ minutes} \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
