[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m **Subject: Technical Analysis and Safety Compliance Evaluation of Sealing Washer Manufacturing Facility**
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Dear [Recipient Name],
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
