[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m So, \(A = -3\), \(B = 1\), and \(C = 0\).
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m The center of the circle is \((1, 2)\). Plugging into the distance formula:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
