[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m So, the distance from the center to the line is approximately 0.316, and the radius of the circle is approximately 3.464. Since 0.316 is less than 3.464, the line intersects the circle at two points. This confirms my earlier conclusion based on the discriminant.
