[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = ‚àö[ ( (‚àö2) )¬≤ + ( (‚àö2) )¬≤ ]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = ‚àö[ 2 + 2 ]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = ‚àö4 = 2
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m So yes, |MN| = 2. That's consistent with our previous result.
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
