[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 3. Each week has 7 days.
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 4. Jenna trains either 3 hours or 5 hours each day.
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 5. The maximum number of 5-hour training days is 5.
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Let me define variables:
