[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m For the shop owner perspective: Print journalism was a key source for:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m - Product recommendations from journalists who covered local businesses
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m - Information about market trends and consumer preferences
