[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m - Using the same area formula:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m   Area = (1/2)|x1(y2 - y3) + x2(y3 - y1) + x3(y1 - y2)|
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Plugging in:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m x1 = z, y1 = s
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m x2 = s, y2 = s
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m x3 = s, y3 = 0
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Area = (1/2)|z*(s - 0) + s*(0 - s) + s*(s - s)|
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = (1/2)| zs + s*(-s) + s*(0) |
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = (1/2)| zs - s¬≤ + 0 |
