[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Vector BZ: Z - B = (z - s, s - 0) = (z - s, s)
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m The cross product in 2D is scalar magnitude given by:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | (e - s)(s) - 0*(z - s) | 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m = | (e - s)s - 0 |
