[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Divide both sides by s (s ‚âÝ 0):
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m (1/2)e = s - e
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
