[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 5. Find equations of lines $DE$ and $BZ$:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m    - Line $DE$: $3x + 2y - 2s = 0$
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m    - Line $BZ$: $3x + 2y - 3s = 0$
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 6. Calculate distance between these lines:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m    - Distance is $\frac{|s|}{\sqrt{13}} = 1$, leading to $s = \sqrt{13}$.
