[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Given that \(| \overrightarrow{OA}| = | \overrightarrow{OB}| = 1\) and \(| \overrightarrow{AB}| = \sqrt{3}\), we need to find the value of \(\overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB}\) and \(| \overrightarrow{OA} + \overrightarrow{OB}|\).
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m First, we use the formula for the magnitude of the difference of two vectors:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | \overrightarrow{AB}|^2 = | \overrightarrow{OA} - \overrightarrow{OB}|^2
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Expanding the right side using the dot product:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | \overrightarrow{OA} - \overrightarrow{OB}|^2 = | \overrightarrow{OA}|^2 + | \overrightarrow{OB}|^2 - 2 \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB}
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Given \(| \overrightarrow{AB}| = \sqrt{3}\), we have:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 3 = 1 + 1 - 2 \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB}
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Solving for \(\overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB}\):
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 3 = 2 - 2 \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB} \implies 1 = -2 \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB} \implies \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB} = -\frac{1}{2}
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Next, we find the magnitude of \(| \overrightarrow{OA} + \overrightarrow{OB}|\) using the dot product formula:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | \overrightarrow{OA} + \overrightarrow{OB}|^2 = | \overrightarrow{OA}|^2 + | \overrightarrow{OB}|^2 + 2 \overrightarrow{OA} \cdot \overrightarrow{OB}
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Substituting the known values:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | \overrightarrow{OA} + \overrightarrow{OB}|^2 = 1 + 1 + 2 \left(-\frac{1}{2}\right) = 2 - 1 = 1
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Thus, the magnitude is:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m | \overrightarrow{OA} + \overrightarrow{OB}| = \sqrt{1} = 1
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \]
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m The final numerical answers are:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m \[
