[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m Let me start by thinking about OSHA guidelines that construction managers might overlook. There are several important ones that don't get as much attention as they should:
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 1. Construction Zone Safety Recommend Practices (CSRP) - These are actually mandatory for OSHA 30-hour programs
[36m(main_task pid=25448)[0m 2. General Guy Wire Rules
